rooms.longDesc: Crown Victorian: This oversized suite features Victorian Style furniture. The bedroom features a king-size, Victorian-styled 4 poster bed, and oversized, heart-shaped 72x72 inch Bath Spa whirlpool bath for 2, surrounded by mirrors and columns right next to the bed. A flat-screen cable television is in between and opposite the bed and bath, for comfortable viewing from both locations. The suite has a telephone, refrigerator, a coffee maker, a make-up table with hairdryer, and an electronic safe.
